      "content": "I understand your frustration, but self-medicating can be risky. Starting St. John's Wort while still on sertraline could lead to unpredictable interactions and side effects. It's not just about knowing your body better; it's about understanding how medications work and how they interact with each other. I strongly advise against making changes to your medication without professional guidance. If you're unable to see your doctor soon, consider reaching out to another healthcare provider or a pharmacist for advice. Your health and safety should always come first.",
